BodyName: Subcommittee on Landmarks, Public Siting and Maritime Uses

Items.Title: Application No. C 150318 PQK submitted by the New York City Human Resources Administration and the Department of Citywide Administrative Services pursuant to Section 197-c of the New York City Charter, for the acquisition of property located at 10300 Foster Avenue for use as a warehouse, Borough of Brooklyn, Community Board 18, Council District 42. This application is subject to the review and action by the Land Use Committee only if appealed to the Council pursuant to 197-d(b)(2) of the Charter or called up by a vote of the Council pursuant to 197-d(b)(3) of the Charter.
Items.ActionText: This Land Use Application was Hearing Held by Committee
